name: The Trees and The Life #007-Prau
description:
You can feel as if the universe trying to flirt with you. They can be romantic sometimes. We didn't expect them gonna show this beautiful scene with sun and Daisy field hill. And then we just feel blessed that day, 5 of us.

The Trees and The Life is a 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
